content: I do not have personal experiences to accurately compare the engineering program at the university of seoul to other top engineering schools in south korea. however, according to various academic rankings, the university of seoul is considered one of the top universities in south korea for engineering education. it is also regarded as a research-oriented university, and its engineering programs are highly respected both within south korea and internationally. some of the other top engineering schools in south korea include the seoul national university, korea advanced institute of science and technology (kaist), pohang university of science and technology (postech), and the korea university.
